results.description:
Draft Writing is a creative text editor for writers and bloggers.
A writing tool to gather your ideas into one place.
Easy writing projects and texts management.

CREATE
- drafts for any blogs, articles, or quick notes;
- writing projects: short stories, novels, poems and more.

GET
- Simple but useful text editor;
- Status labels to show the current status of a project;
- Possibility to add inspirational photos of places and characters to your projects;
- Possibility to store unlimited number of documents;
- Handy document organization;
- Article preview;
- Exporting articles you are working on to rich-text format (.rtf).

Optimize your work and improve your productivity with Draft Writing - Creative Text Editor! Keep focused on what matters the most!


